  {
    "language": "Urdu",
    "translator": "Dr. Tahir ul Qadri",
    "text": "اور  ( اپنے در کے )  کسی منگتے کو نہ جھڑکیں"
  },
  {
    "language": "Hindi",
    "translator": "Moulana Palanpuri",
    "text": "और जो माँगता हो उसे न झिझकना,"
  },
  {
    "language": "English Sahih International",
    "translator": "",
    "text": "And as for the petitioner, do not repel [him]."
  },
  {
    "language": "English",
    "translator": "Muhammad Junagarhi",
    "text": "And as for the petitioner, do not repel [him]."
  },
  {
    "language": "English",
    "translator": "Abul A'la Maudoodi",
    "text": "and chide not him who asks,"
